g.text: Quincy told me he'd kill me if I ever told anyone this story

g.text: ok, so we were on this mission to sabotage Scaldra weapon production. I was doing the metalwork, Quincy had my back, watching for any patrols.

g.title: j3204631943
g.text: I'm sure.

g.text: k! can't say I blame u

g.title: j1528615926
g.text: Sorry, was that a typo? I'm sure you meant "we got stopped by a bunch of SCALDRA who recognized Quincy instantly."

g.title: j2493537675
g.text: Oh no. Those poor kids must have been terrified.

g.title: j1527116819
g.text: Kids?

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.text: u heard me!

g.text: Used colorful language and no uncertain terms to tell them to get out of his way?

g.title: j2126010009
g.text: Ignored them?

g.title: j139418352

g.text: Those kids must have adored him.

g.text: They knew him from POSITIVE interactions?

g.title: j3788263299

g.text: So, Quincy went on a side quest to find a tammpet for some Höllvanian kid?

g.text: He... said that?

g.title: j188014356
g.text: You're definitely kidding.

g.title: j921389743
g.text: I swear on Zeke's life!

g.title: j4050247249
g.text: Quincy actually pulled one of those little digital pet things out of his pocket and gave it to the kid.

g.title: j154623204
g.text: Sol only knows how long he'd had it, or how long he'd spent searching through Höllvania to find it

g.title: j2352386255
g.text: once that funny little horned creature appeared on the screen, I don't know who was smiling bigger. the kid or Quincy seeing the kid so happy

g.title: j3972133901
g.text: Boolean QuincyLovesKids is now true.

g.title: j416832823
g.text: You know, now that I'm picturing it, that really does sound like him.

g.title: j3940333111
g.text: You'll have to excuse me for finding this story hard to believe.

g.title: j2651719028
g.text: You're lucky you got to see that side of him. I bet few people ever do.

g.title: j1368315502

g.title: j2866617876
